# AI Professor 🎓🤖

**AI Professor** is an intelligent educational web application designed
to assist students with learning, note-taking, quizzes, PDF analysis,
and AI-powered academic support. It acts as a virtual professor that
helps students study smarter through interactive AI features powered by
Google's Gemini AI.

# 🚀 Live Features

-   AI Chat Professor
-   Smart Notes Generator
-   AI Quiz Generator
-   PDF Upload & Question Answering
-   Download Notes as PDF
-   Learning Progress Tracker
-   Activity History Dashboard
-   Voice-enabled Learning Support
-   Modern Responsive Dashboard UI

# 📚 About the Project

AI Professor is a student-focused educational platform that provides
instant academic assistance using Artificial Intelligence. The platform
allows students to interact with an AI tutor, generate study notes,
create quizzes, analyze PDF documents, and track their learning progress
in one centralized dashboard.

The primary objective of this project is to make learning: - Faster -
Interactive - Personalized - Accessible - AI-driven

# ✨ Key Features

## 🤖 AI Professor Chat

-   Ask academic questions
-   Get detailed explanations
-   Receive examples and study-friendly answers
-   Supports multiple subjects

## 📝 Smart Notes Generator

Generate structured study notes including: - Topic Definition -
Important Concepts - Examples - Applications - Summary - Bullet-point
explanations

## ❓ AI Quiz Generator

Automatically generates: - Multiple Choice Questions - Four options per
question - Correct answers - Difficulty-based quizzes

## 📄 PDF Study Assistant

Users can: - Upload PDF documents - Ask questions related to uploaded
PDFs - Receive AI-generated answers based on document content

## 📥 Download Notes

-   Export generated notes into PDF format
-   Useful for revision and offline learning

## 📊 Learning Analytics

Tracks: - Number of chats - Notes generated - Quizzes created - PDFs
analyzed

## 🕒 Activity Tracker

Maintains recent activity history including: - Chat sessions - Notes
generation - Quiz generation - PDF uploads

## 🎙️ Voice Learning Support

-   Voice-enabled interaction
-   Improves accessibility and learning experience

# 💡 Unique Features

Unlike traditional educational websites, AI Professor combines multiple
AI-powered educational tools into a single platform.

### Unique aspects include:

-   AI Tutor + Notes Generator + Quiz Generator in one platform
-   PDF Question Answering System
-   Automatic Notes to PDF Conversion
-   Personalized Learning Dashboard
-   Activity Tracking System
-   Student-friendly AI responses
-   Modern and responsive interface
-   Lightweight Flask architecture

# 🛠️ Technologies Used

## Frontend

-   HTML5
-   CSS3
-   JavaScript

## Backend

-   Python
-   Flask
-   Flask-CORS

## Artificial Intelligence

-   Google Gemini AI API
-   Gemini 2.5 Flash Model

## PDF Processing

-   PyPDF

## PDF Generation

-   ReportLab

## Deployment

-   Render
-   GitHub

# 📂 Project Structure

``` text
