```

# ⚙️ Installation

``` bash
git clone https://github.com/kalyanramgeda/ai-professor.git
cd ai-professor/backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Create a `.env` file:

``` env
GEMINI_API_KEY=YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY
```

Run:

``` bash
python app.py
```

Open: `http://127.0.0.1:5000`

